# ZOKARIO /files/ — paid deliverables
# IMPORTANT: on a static host this directory CANNOT be truly protected.
# The unguessable filenames + no listing + noindex below are a speed bump,
# not security. The real fix is signed, expiring download URLs issued by the
# fulfilment backend (stripe-backend/webhook.php step 3); at that point move
# these files out of public hosting entirely.

# No directory listing: filenames are unguessable, so the listing is the
# only practical way to enumerate them.
Options -Indexes

# Keep every file here out of search engines and link previews.
<IfModule mod_headers.c>
  Header set X-Robots-Tag "noindex, nofollow, noarchive"
</IfModule>

# Do not let referrers leak the unguessable URLs onward.
<IfModule mod_headers.c>
  Header set Referrer-Policy "no-referrer"
</IfModule>
